last_episode_to_air.name: Ruby The Superfan
last_episode_to_air.overview: Andy's sister Ruby wants to meet her hero, superstar vlogger, Fay Moss, so Andy and the Band stage a fashion photo shoot.  Will Fay turn out to be all that Ruby had hoped for?

name: Andy And The Band
overview: Andy and the Band risk missing their next gig by taking on super-weird Odd Jobs for their fans. A madcap mix of songs, slapstick and silliness.
